<li>Exzellenzcluster <a href="https://www.uni-hamburg.de/forschung/forschungsprofil/exzellenzcluster/understanding-written-artefacts.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">„Understanding Written Artefacts“</a></li>
